************************************************************************
* 1. GENERAL INFORMATIONS
************************************************************************

What: 			Texturepack for Minetest
Size: 			128x128 pixel
author: 		kddekadenz
sources of textures: 	opengameart.org;  Golgotha; burnigwell.org; wikipedia.com


************************************************************************
* 2. INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS
************************************************************************

2.1 Linux Mint

-Extract the archive
-Copy and paste all of the textures from the 'data' folder into /usr/share/minetest (be sure to open the folder as admin) and overwrite the old textures 
	-> IMPORTANT: don't forget to make a backup of your old textures
-Start the game and enjoy



2.2 Windows

-Extract the archive
-Copy and paste all of the textures from the 'data' folder into the 'data' folder in your Minetest folder and overwrite the old textures 
	-> IMPORTANT: don't forget to make a backup of your old textures
-Start the game and enjoy


2.3 Cross Platform

- locate your minetest.conf
- add to it: texture_path = <insert location of the AdventurePack data folder here>


